r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Shanghai SIPG - Tianjin Quanjian</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1849","checkdouble":"192439"},{"date":"06:48 01/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/8: Sao Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sao Real mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Pochettino \u201c\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\u201d Mourinho, \u2018H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 Barca mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/8.</h2><h2>Modric mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Inter Milan. T\u1edd Sky Italia cho bi\u1ebft b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Modric c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 33, n\u01a1i anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 Brozovic, Ivan Perisic.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18 Modric mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18 Modric mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-Modric-muon-thanh-doi-thu-cua-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Modric mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino \u201c\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\u201d Mourinho<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tottenham cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB nh\u01b0 HLV Mourinho. \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u00e1y m\u00f3c. S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t l\u1eabn tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ec7c v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian b\u00ean gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8\", Mauricio Pochettino chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u2018H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 Barca mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd SPORT, Yerry Mina \u01b0u ti\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp M.U h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Everton trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111a\u0303 bo\u0309 theo do\u0303i ta\u0300i khoa\u0309n cu\u0309a Barcelona, \u0111\u00f4\u0300ng th\u01a1\u0300i chuy\u00ea\u0309n h\u01b0\u01a1\u0301ng theo do\u0303i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U cu\u0303ng nh\u01b0 Paul Pogba hay Antonio Valencia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Barca. Anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Kante s\u1eafp h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t Chelsea<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>\r\n<!--[endif]--><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, N'Golo Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd The Times\u00a0\u0111\u01b0a tin, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t b\u1eb1ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 380 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4la/tu\u1ea7n, ngang Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a Man Utd. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t Stamford Bridge.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Milan m\u01b0\u1ee3n Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ronaldo, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan. Theo \u0111o\u0301, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina\u00a0se\u0303 chuy\u00ea\u0309n t\u01a1\u0301i thi \u0111\u00e2\u0301u cho AC Milan \u01a1\u0309 mu\u0300a gia\u0309i 2018/19\u00a0t\u01a1\u0301i b\u0103\u0300ng ba\u0309n h\u01a1\u0323p \u0111\u00f4\u0300ng cho m\u01b0\u01a1\u0323n, co\u0301 th\u01a1\u0300i ha\u0323n 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m\u00a0\u0111i\u00ea\u0300u khoa\u0309n mua \u0111\u01b0\u0301t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan se\u0303 tr\u1ea3 cho Juventus s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n\u00a018 tri\u00ea\u0323u euro \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n\u00a0Gonzalo\u00a0Higuain,\u00a0c\u00f4\u0323ng th\u00eam \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u khoa\u0309n mua \u0111\u01b0\u0301t tri\u0323 gia\u0301 37 tri\u00ea\u0323u euro khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Williian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi\u00a0Globo Esporte\u00a0m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Willian \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai: \"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf London. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.\u00a0T\u00f4i s\u1eafp s\u1eeda tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi gian qua, Chelsea t\u1eebng 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barcelona d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ngo\u00e0i ra, M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Juve v\u00ec mua Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Napoli,\u00a0De Laurentiis, cho r\u1eb1ng\u00a0Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00ec\u00a0\u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i\u00a0nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ronaldo\u00a0\u0111ang gi\u00e0 \u0111i. \u0110\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m cho m\u1ed9t CLB n\u1ebfu chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0\u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1eb7ng cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua quy m\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Juventus. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n hay th\u1ec3 thao nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3, s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n n\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n\", ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch\u00a0De Laurentiis nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp chia tay sao x\u1ecbt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady, Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Danny Drinkwater tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Leicester City v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Drinkwater \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge do nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean mi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh, \u00edt h\u01a1n t\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Danny Drinkwater v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.\u00a0<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-317-mourinho-duoc-chieu-long-bang-2-bom-tan-184-192358.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xem th\u00eam: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7: Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng b\u1eb1ng 2 bom t\u1ea5n</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1848","checkdouble":"192440"},{"date":"15:47 31/07","title":"Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/7/everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/Everton-muon-mua-Marcos-Rojo-cua-MU-voi-gia-cuc-soc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Mourinho \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm Harry Maguire ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a M.U, n\u1ebfu Marcos Rojo ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Rojo, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-172-192177.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wolves mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Rojo</span>,\u00a0Watford, Everton v\u00e0 West Ham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/Everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Marco Silva mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton, Marcos Rojo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi M.U, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo, Everton c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Mina c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1847","checkdouble":"192398"},{"date":"15:12 31/07","title":"Guardiola m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho sao tr\u1ebb Man City ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-harrison.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 gia nh\u1eadp Leeds United c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i Marcelo Bielsa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harrison t\u1edbi Leeds tu nghi\u1ec7p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJack Harrison t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i hai h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 Man United. N\u0103m 14 tu\u1ed5i, anh theo gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf New York City, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 chung ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0 t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n City Football Group v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Harrison \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n giao cho Man City song l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Middlesbrough m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Anh ra s\u00e2n 4 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Leeds h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Leeds h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-harrison.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Harrison t\u1edbi Leeds thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ee3t du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Harrison \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 b\u1eaft t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng trai s\u1eafp tr\u00f2n 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. M\u1edbi h\u00f4m qua, Harrison \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Leeds United \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep Guardiola th\u01b0\u1eddng chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Marcelo Bielsa c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Leeds c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Jack Harrison ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola\" title=\"Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-hoc-tro-du-de-thua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola v\u1ec1 Marcelo Bielsa v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi kh\u00edch l\u1ec7\u201d, Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Leeds. \u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Pep \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Bielsa. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Leeds. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Elland Road, cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola-172-191855.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u kh\u1ecfi \u00e1ch Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sau-mahrez-man-city-sap-co-them-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro-172-191834.html\">Sau Mahrez, Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep-172-191782.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1846","checkdouble":"192399"},{"date":"16:32 31/07","title":"Tottenham nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u01a1 b\u1eafp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/tottenham-phai-mua-kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Denis Suarez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao Sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 18 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 500 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-co-the-chia-tay-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, song thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Denis Suarez n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 20 \u0111\u1ebfn 25 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia v\u00e0 Sevilla \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, 21 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Dortmund, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou song ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Grizmann v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rafinha</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRafinha kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Inter Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rafinha\" title=\"Rafinha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/rafinha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rafinha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n gi\u1eefa Rafinha v\u00e0 Inter Milan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u1ec9 ghi 2 b\u00e0n sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, Inter \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Rafinha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca, song t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Paco Alcacer</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Luis Suarez, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 17 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paco Alcacer\" title=\"Paco Alcacer\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/acaser.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paco Alcacer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Barca c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay. Paco Alcacer kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u00ednh b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t Paco Alcacer, Barc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Bilbao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andre Gomes\" title=\"Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Andre Gomes c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Andre Gomes</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Gomes n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Aleix Vidal<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, 28 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleix Vidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, anh hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aleix Vidal\" title=\"Aleix Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aleix Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSergi Roberto v\u00e0 Nelson Semedo c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Aleix Vidal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Inter Milan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Aleix Vidal, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7, 33 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Thomas Vermaelen ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1000 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Umtiti v\u00e0 Pique. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" title=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vemar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Clement Lenglet, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Theo Sport, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Crystal Palace v\u00e0 Watford \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Vermaelen tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1845","checkdouble":"192400"},{"date":"16:43 31/07","title":"Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/antonio-conte-hai-nam-nem-trai-du-hi-no-ai-o-cung-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec7m k\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Mourinho, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Mourinho, Scolari, Villas-Boas v\u00e0 Conte. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1eddi Chelsea theo m\u1ed9t \u201ck\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\u201d ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau: t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wembley t\u1ed1i 19/5, Chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA, Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Manchester United 1-0 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11m c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, v\u1edbi n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1i r\u00f3i khi n\u00e2ng cao danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 \u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte: Hai nam nem trai du Hi No Ai O cung Chelsea1\" title=\"Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/co.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 13/7, t\u1ee9c 25 ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng Chelsea v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA, Conte ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb&nbsp; BL\u0110 The Blues sa th\u1ea3i, k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1eafc m\u00e0u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Gi\u1edd Conte \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ean l\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Gi\u1edd The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh HLV m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00e1c - Maurizio Sarri. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, c\u00e1c True Blues s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn k\u00ed \u1ee9c n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 Conte?&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t Conte h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch? M\u1ed9t Conte t\u00e0i ba h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh 3-4-3 (c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn chu\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2016/17? M\u1ed9t Conte &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed9c t\u00e0i&rdquo; qua tin nh\u1eafn&hellip; y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Diego Costa t\u00ecm CLB kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t Conte sa l\u1ea7y trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ea9u chi\u1ebfn cay nghi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Stamford Bridge &ndash; Jose Mourinho. Hay m\u1ed9t Conte c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Conte trong tim c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u00e0&hellip; Conte n\u00e0o th\u00ec n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia hay chia tay \u00f4ng, h\u1eb3n \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c True Bules s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn v\u1ebf th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t. B\u1edfi h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u1eddi Roman Abramovich ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Conte \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt &ldquo;Conte&rdquo; nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 sau Conte ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u &ldquo;Conte&rdquo; n\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf HLV \u1edf Stamford Bridge l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 xa x\u1ec9!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa thai HLV Antonio Conte truoc them mua giai moi.\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Thuc-hu-chuyen-Antonio-Conte-dan-dat-AC-Milan-thay-Gattuso-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau Conte, Sarri l\u00e0 HLV th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong v\u00f2ng 5 n\u0103m qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 l\u01b0\u1ee3t HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft The Blues trong tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0 Ray Wilkins hay Steve Holland. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng hay vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Chelsea s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ec3 chia tay HLV m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng &ldquo;tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0 Conte!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1ec1 n\u1ed5i. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u xa lu\u00f4n b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng &ndash; m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa HLV Chelsea v\u00e0 Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB. T\u1ec9 ph\u00fa Abramovich l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Chelsea th\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, bi\u1ebfn The Blues t\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 l\u00e0 1 CLB h\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 90 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh 1 trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1eeb 2003. Nh\u01b0ng Abramovich c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0103n h\u00f3a d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t Stamford Bridge khi\u1ebfn The Blues kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh nh\u01b0 United, Liverpool hay Arsenal. M\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0103n h\u00f3a coi HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thu\u00ea cho Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec7m k\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Mourinho, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Mourinho, Scolari, Villas-Boas v\u00e0 Conte. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1eddi Chelsea theo m\u1ed9t &ldquo;k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau: t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea thay Conte b\u1eb1ng HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u00f3 t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec1 &ldquo;C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ph\u00eda sau \u0110\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 V\u1ef1c s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Conte \u1edf Chelsea&rdquo; \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean Express h\u00f4m 13/6 &ndash; \u0111\u00fang 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Simon Johnson vi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00e1ch v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00e1c \u0111a s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Anh. Conte bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y H\u00e8 2016. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau khi gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier Laegue 2016/17 trong ho\u00e0nh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb CLB \u1edf c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Conte tin r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd \u00f4ng ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Conte \u0111\u00e3 sai. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Conte v\u1edbi BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. Conte th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ec9 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&rdquo;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3n th\u1ea7y&rdquo;, &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 gh\u1ebf HLV&rdquo;, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i khi Chelsea c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e2m nguy, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u00e1c fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb ng\u1eef nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 The Blues. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 th\u1eadt, ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u1ed1 1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7t HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00f3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p. Nh\u01b0 bao \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Conte c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u1ea5y trong h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte trong tran Chelsea 1-0 MU chung ket FA Cup 2017/18\" title=\"Antonio Conte trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Zinedine-Zidane-tu-chuc-HLV-truong-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Costa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Conte kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi sau v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m &ldquo;tin nh\u1eafn cho ngh\u1ec9&rdquo; h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, Willian d\u00f9ng c\u00fap che m\u1eb7t Conte trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. Courtois, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Sarri gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 d\u00f9 Conte&ndash; tr\u00ean danh ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf - v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u00f3m d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Mario Balotelli hay Hatem Ben Arfa, m\u1ea5y khi d\u00e1m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00f3ng Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB? \u0110\u1eddi Conte c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady tr\u00ean t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t HLV, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb thu\u00ea \u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay Conte \u0111\u00f3n sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 49 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i r\u1ea5t xa Chelsea, sau 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7y b\u00e3o t\u00e1p \u1edf Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Sarri \u1edf v\u00e0o ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 Conte hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i? Hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng bi \u0111\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>ELFLACO (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1844","checkdouble":"192401"},{"date":"17:24 31/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i gia NHA xem Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/28/chelsea-muon-mua-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. HLV Maurizio Sarri trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a Lewandowski v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina l\u1ea1i \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Bundesliga ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chelsea-muon-mua-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Chelsea, h\u1ecd \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Alvaro Morata g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 sau 1 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge trong khi Olivier Giroud kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. The Blues \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Bayern Munich ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Lewandowski. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Dortmund v\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u1edbi t\u1eadn 4 n\u0103m m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Trong 126 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 qua, Lewandowski ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 106 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Lewandowski\" title=\"tien dao Lewandowski\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/28/chelsea-muon-mua-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bayern c\u1ed1 gi\u1eef Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 9 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi CLB, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i\u201d, Kovac n\u00f3i. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRobert mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga, \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois-172-192377.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/leicester-muon-mua-lai-drinkwater-172-192356.html\">Leicester mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Drinkwater kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chap-nhan-chi-65-trieu-bang-mua-pulisic-172-192340.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Dortmund</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1843","checkdouble":"192403"}]}